results.title: Avengers (1998) #500
results.description: AVENGERS DISASSEMBLED BEGINS HERE! The powerhouse team of Brian Michael Bendis and David Finch take on Earth's Mightiest Heroes in this double-sized anniversary issue!   It begins with the return of an Avenger thought dead--and by the time it's over, everything you know about the Avengers will have changed! AN EVENT THAT WILL ROCK THE ENTIRETY OF THE MARVEL UNIVERSE -- AND IT ALL STARTS HERE, TRUE BELIEVER!

textObjects.text: BENDIIIIS! In this landmark anniversary issue, the writer unleashed an undead Jack of Hearts—killing Ant Man Scott Lang, made Tony feel like he'd been drinking again, crashed a Quinjet, made Vision vomit multiple Ultron duplicates, turned She-Hulk into a rampaging monster—tearing Vision in half...Yikes!
